'''Plovdiv''' ([[kirilikanes]]: Пловдив) si o duito baro [[foro]] andar i [[Bulgariya]]. Si o xulyaripnasko mashkar andar o [[Oblast Plovdiv]] pi sudutni Bulgariya vi o bareder foro andar i puranipnaski rig [[Trachiya]].

==Phuvipen==
O foro si pe efta playa (akana ekh sas telyardo), pi len [[Marica]].

[[Image:Plovdiv-view-gruev.JPG|left|thumb|250px|A view over Plovdiv]]

==Puranipen==
Ando than le forosko Plovdiv, manusha beshen andar o 7500to [[bersh]] p.X. (opretele). Po vaxt le [[trakurya|trakurengo]] lesko nav sas ''Eumolpiya''. 342to bersheste p.X. o thagar [[Filip 2to la Machedoniyako]], mardyas le trakurya thai xulayardyas o foro, navyardo ''Filippoupolis'', ([[latinikanes]]: ''Filippopolis'')

